Package no.hiof.larseknu.game

Class PlayerCharacter

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.hiof.larseknu.game.PlayerCharacter
  • public class PlayerCharacter
extends java.lang.Object
    PlayableCharacter is a class that represent a playable character in the game. Holds information about the name, nickName, level, noob status, health and current weapons.
